	(text "PSU ±24V — Component Placement Guide\n\nSchematic flow (left to right):\n\n1. TR_main secondary (2×18VAC) enters from left\n2. BR1 bridge rectifier → raw ±25.5V DC\n3. C_main1/C_main2 (4700µF) → smooth DC\n4. LM317T (+24V) / LM337T (-24V) regulators\n   R_adj=240R, R_adj_b=4.32K, trim=500R\n   Vout = 1.25 × (1 + R_adj_b/R_adj) = 24.0V\n5. C_main3/C_main4 (4700µF) → post-reg filter\n6. Output: +24V, -24V, GND"
		(at 25.4 25.4 0)
		(effects (font (size 1.524 1.524)) (justify left))
		(uuid "f1000001-psu-text-0001-000000000001")
	)
